high_descs: Turn around and walk to the phone next to the box on the couch.
Pick up the phone next to the box.
Walk to the box on the couch closest to you.
Place the phone in the box on the couch.
Pick up the box on the couch.
Turn left and walk to the black desk with a white vase on it.
Place the box to the right of the vase on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a phone in it to the right of the white vase on the black desk.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white box on the sofa.
Pick up the phone from next to the white box.
Turn right and take one step, then turn left and face the box on the sofa.
Put the phone in the white box.
Pick up the white box from the sofa.
Turn around and walk to the black desk and face it.
Set the white box on the black desk.
anns.task_desc: Put the phone in the box and set the box on the desk.

high_descs: Move to the couch behind you
Pick up a phone from the couch
Move to the box to the right of you
Place the phone inside the box
Pick up the box from the couch
Move to the black desk to the left of you
Place the box on top of the desk
anns.task_desc: Put a box from the couch with a phone in it on the black desk.
